505
00:41:10,468 --> 00:41:14,096
<i>Now the issues that should be discussed</i>
<i>are social security, tax reform,</i>

506
00:41:14,180 --> 00:41:16,640
<i>foreign policy, and national security.</i>

507
00:41:16,724 --> 00:41:17,683
Mm.

508
00:41:19,810 --> 00:41:22,021
<i>A lot of issues should be discussed,</i>

509
00:41:22,104 --> 00:41:24,648
<i>but instead,</i>
<i>they're trying to distract the public and…</i>

510
00:41:24,732 --> 00:41:25,733
I'm listening.

511
00:41:28,110 --> 00:41:30,946
<i>I wanted to give you an update</i>
<i>on the case concerning the article.</i>

512
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:34,408
It certainly is taking a very long time.

513
00:41:35,159 --> 00:41:37,786
You know that I only want
to hear good news, right?

514
00:41:37,870 --> 00:41:40,998
- I've told you that before.
<i>- Yes, I completely understand.</i>

515
00:41:41,081 --> 00:41:44,627
<i>I'm very sorry to have to tell you this,</i>
<i>but they've taken a firm stance</i>

516
00:41:44,710 --> 00:41:47,463
<i>and are determined to fight back</i>
<i>until the end.</i>

517
00:41:47,546 --> 00:41:49,882
<i>There's not much we can do at this point,</i>
<i>I'm afraid.</i>

518
00:41:49,965 --> 00:41:53,010
<i>The situation is extremely tricky,</i>
<i>and we'll…</i>
